Camera - Class in <Unnamed>
Camera Used for following the player around the World This is a simple class which keeps track of the player as they move around the map, making sure the viewport is centered on them.
Camera(double, double, int, int, int, int) - Constructor for class Camera
This constructor receives a lot of arguments, which it then stores, but this is preferable to having to pass them every single time update is called since they're all constants.

checkItemCollision(ArrayList<Item>) - Method in class Racer
